    <Text>第二天，汤姆练习了一些咒语。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26173</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他试着变出一些石砖来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47661</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>噗！奶酪砖出现了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57109</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>骑士来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57110</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66325</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>骑士四处看了看，猫咪躲了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73050</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你能把这些砖头变成金子吗？”骑士问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73051</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77779</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个骑士很贪婪。”汤姆想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77780</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你有一次免费魔法咒语。”汤姆说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82004</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85070</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你只想要一些金砖？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85071</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88839</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯。”骑士说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88840</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98426</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在实验室里走了一圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98427</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108546</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆看到他偷了一些奶酪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108547</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113672</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不喜欢这个骑士。”汤姆想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113673</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想在比赛中获胜。”骑士最后说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118915</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122113</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望得到奖金，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122114</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但我的马不听我的话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126104</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133195</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你施个咒语让它听话。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133196</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137831</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>比赛在皇家活动上举行。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137832</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141778</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>骑士握着缰绳，骑着马。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141779</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148847</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们都尽力想打倒对方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148848</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154590</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，留在马上的骑士获胜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154591</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157224</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆皱起了眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157225</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159123</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这不公平。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165046</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我抽到了一次免费魔法卡。”骑士厉声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165047</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你必须按我说的做，魔法师！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆又皱起了眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175382</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>骑士坏笑着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175383</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以把我的卡卖给德克。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186330</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是个秃子，但他抽到了免费的理发卡！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186331</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190495</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190496</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196592</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧。午夜时，来赛场见我。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196593</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204530</EndMilliseconds>
